1. Used component based architecture for building
2. Used Angular CDK for drag and drop functionality
3. Optimized for all screen sizes including mobile, tablet, desktop and large screens

Functoinalities implemented:
    + Adding new List
    + Reordering lists within boards using drag and drop
    + Adding new card
    + Reordering cards within list using drag and drop
    + Scrolling within list if list height exceeds viewport
    + Scrolling beyond if list width exceeds viewport
    + Delete created list
    + Opening modal popup on card click
    + Delete created card
    + Add comments for a card